Third-party attributions
========================

This project depends on a number of third-party open-source crates
(Rust) and npm packages (TypeScript/JavaScript). Each is governed by
its own license; the full set of attributions is generated at release
time and shipped alongside the signed binaries.

To regenerate the full third-party NOTICE locally:

  Rust crates:
    cargo install cargo-about
    cargo about generate -m agent/Cargo.toml about.hbs > NOTICE-AGENT
    cargo about generate -m frontend/src-tauri/Cargo.toml about.hbs > NOTICE-TAURI

  npm packages:
    npx license-checker --production --csv > NOTICE-FRONTEND.csv

These outputs are not committed; they are produced as part of the
release pipeline and attached to the GitHub Release as
THIRD-PARTY-NOTICES.{txt,csv}.

